+/*
+ * Renesas R-Car SRU/SCU/SSIU/SSI support
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2013 Renesas Solutions Corp.
+ * Kuninori Morimoto <kuninori.morimoto.gx@renesas.com>
+ *
+ * Based on fsi.c
+ * Kuninori Morimoto <morimoto.kuninori@renesas.com>
